Check-property-is-there-or-not_key1: name: Check property is there or not
Check-property-is-there-or-not_key2: You can check whether property exists or not in an object. We can use the .hasOwnProperty(propname) method of objects to determine if that object has the given property name. .hasOwnProperty() returns `true` or `false` if the property is found or not.
